# Hivemind dev stack. Run with `make dev` (which also brings up Postgres).
#
# - web: FastAPI app - Mailgun webhook + admin UI. Binds to ${HOST:-127.0.0.1}
#   and ${PORT:-18788} — set PORT in .env to override. Tailscale Funnel
#   proxies the public :10000 (in MAILGUN_WEBHOOK_URL) to this local port.
# - worker: Procrastinate worker — picks up run_agent + curate_memory jobs.
#   Runs under watchfiles so code edits in src/ restart the worker.
#   Sends real Mailgun replies. Set EMAIL_AGENT_WORKER_DRY_RUN=true on the
#   worker line to suppress sends during local testing.
web: uv run email-agent web
worker: uv run email-agent worker-dev
